<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:45:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>我们对现实的认识可能完全错误</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/we-might-be-completely-wrong-about-reality</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:45:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/we-might-be-completely-wrong-about-reality</guid></item><item><title>7 岁男孩在婴儿时期患上这种疾病多年后，死于世界上最具传染性的疾病引起的脑部疾病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/boy-7-dies-of-brain-condition-caused-by-worlds-most-contagious-disease-years-after-he-had-it-as-a-baby</link><description>麻疹是一种高度传染性的病毒感染，会导致高烧、咳嗽、眼睛发红/流泪以及特征性的斑疹，通过空气中的飞沫传播。它主要影响儿童，但也可能袭击任何人，严重情况下会导致肺炎、脑肿胀或死亡。预防主要通过 MMR 疫苗进行，有效率达 97%。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/boy-7-dies-of-brain-condition-caused-by-worlds-most-contagious-disease-years-after-he-had-it-as-a-baby.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/boy-7-dies-of-brain-condition-caused-by-worlds-most-contagious-disease-years-after-he-had-it-as-a-baby</guid></item><item><title>Unity 扩展对 Steam、SteamOS 和 Linux 的官方支持</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unity-extends-official-support-for-steam-steamos-linux</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unity-extends-official-support-for-steam-steamos-linux</guid></item><item><title>“计算权”法案在众议院获得通过，而提议的数据中心预防措施失败</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/right-to-compute-bill-passes-house-while-proposed-data-center-precautions-flop</link><description>在周三和周四的两个拥挤的会议日中，新罕布什尔州众议院继续对技术监管采取不干涉的态度。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/right-to-compute-bill-passes-house-while-proposed-data-center-precautions-flop.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/right-to-compute-bill-passes-house-while-proposed-data-center-precautions-flop</guid></item><item><title>C9orf72 六核苷酸重复 RNA 通过全基因组 DNA 驱动转录失调：RNA 杂合 G-四链体</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/c9orf72-hexanucleotide-repeat-rna-drives-transcriptional-dysregulation-through-genome-wide-dna-rna-hybrid-g-quadruplexes</link><description>ALS 中的转录失调六核苷酸重复&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/c9orf72-hexanucleotide-repeat-rna-drives-transcriptional-dysregulation-through-genome-wide-dna-rna-hybrid-g-quadruplexes2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 11:45:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/c9orf72-hexanucleotide-repeat-rna-drives-transcriptional-dysregulation-through-genome-wide-dna-rna-hybrid-g-quadruplexes</guid></item><item><title>数学家找到了一个 pi 公式来统治所有这些</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mathematicians-find-one-pi-formula-to-rule-them-all</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 11:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/mathematicians-find-one-pi-formula-to-rule-them-all</guid></item><item><title>PCIF1 介导的 ACC 神经元 m6Am 修饰参与炎症性疼痛和焦虑</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pcif1-mediated-m6am-modification-in-acc-neurons-participates-in-inflammatory-pain-and-anxiety</link><description>刘等人。证明 ACC 神经元中的 m6Am 甲基转移酶 PCIF1 对于炎性疼痛和共病焦虑的引发和维持至关重要。他们进一步揭示，PCIF1 通过靶向 Gap43 m6Am 修饰来调节这些行为，从而促进 GAP43 表达。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pcif1-mediated-m6am-modification-in-acc-neurons-participates-in-inflammatory-pain-and-anxiety.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 11:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pcif1-mediated-m6am-modification-in-acc-neurons-participates-in-inflammatory-pain-and-anxiety</guid></item><item><title>交互式斑马鱼胚胎单细胞图谱</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/interactive-zebrafish-embryo-single-cell-atlas</link><description>基因和细胞的发育图谱。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/interactive-zebrafish-embryo-single-cell-atlas3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 11:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/interactive-zebrafish-embryo-single-cell-atlas</guid></item><item><title>新生儿先天淋巴细胞功能和发育多样性的单细胞转录参考</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-single-cell-transcriptional-reference-for-the-functional-and-developmental-diversity-of-neonatal-innate-lymphoid-cells</link><description>通过 Ficoll 梯度从新鲜脐带血 (CB) 中分离单核细胞 (MNC)（ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-single-cell-transcriptional-reference-for-the-functional-and-developmental-diversity-of-neonatal-innate-lymphoid-cells2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 10:45:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-single-cell-transcriptional-reference-for-the-functional-and-developmental-diversity-of-neonatal-innate-lymphoid-cells</guid></item><item><title>运动皮层细胞类型特异性 TDP-43 病理学</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cell-type-specific-tdp-43-pathology-in-the-motor-cortex</link><description>癌症的标志包括在人类肿瘤的多步发展过程中获得的六种生物学能力。这些特征构成了合理化肿瘤疾病复杂性的组织原则。它们包括维持增殖信号、逃避生长抑制剂、抵抗细胞死亡、实现复制永生、诱导血管生成以及激活侵袭和转移。这些标志的背后是基因组不稳定性和炎症，基因组不稳定性会产生加速其获得的遗传多样性，而炎症会促进多种标志功能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cell-type-specific-tdp-43-pathology-in-the-motor-cortex2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 10:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cell-type-specific-tdp-43-pathology-in-the-motor-cortex</guid></item></channel></